# TESAIoT firmware and Bitstream (external workspaces)

Firmware truth is **not** vendored in Bitstream-Studio. When the task mentions protocol fields, encoders, or MCU behavior, check:

| Role | Path |
|------|------|
| **Main firmware** | `D:\CODE\2026\TESAIoT_PSoC_Edge_Workspace\TESAIoT_Firmware` |
| **Library** | `D:\CODE\2026\TESAIoT_PSoC_Edge_Workspace\TESAIoT_Library` |
| **Bitstream module (authoritative)** | `D:\CODE\2026\TESAIoT_PSoC_Edge_Workspace\TESAIoT_Library\CM55\modules\bitstream` |
| **Host BS2 encode/decode** | `extension/src/bitstream2/` |

**bitstream-simulator** — separate repo / VS Code extension (not under Bitstream-Studio). Install separately for Simulator telemetry.

Communication: **Thai and/or English** only.
